"adj. (指毛发或衣服)凌乱的 【英】 adj.(指毛发或衣服) 凌乱的(untidy of hair or clothing) adj. 头发凌乱的; 衣冠不整的 = untidy 【记】heve = hair头发dis离开, hevel = heaven天堂: 从天堂上掉下来－凌乱的 【记】dis去掉 + heavy重，将很重的东西放下，运动员举重后放下时毛发与衣服是凌乱的 disheveled (adj.)  also dishevelled, early 15c., ""without dressed hair,"" parallel form of dishevel (adj.); see dishevel. General sense of ""with disordered dress"" is from c.1600."
